::Battera::

She was flying along side CyberShark.  She saw the forest and valleys below. 
  She didn't want to talk.  She just wanted to get this over with.  She knew 
that she could never forgive herself, so why should Vulios forgive her.  She 
just flew and kept up with CyberShark.  She looked around, she wondered 
where that big red flyer went to. She shook her head, it didn't matter.  
hardly anything mattered anymore to her.
